CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 3, 1966. pg. 13A, reads: "Adorable Pair - All eyes were on this adorable pair when they performed in a 'Tom Thumb Wedding' recently. The little 'bride' is Carol Dillingham, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Cleveland Dillingham.  The 'groom' is Robert Goggins, son of the Robert Goggins, all of East Liberty. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Tom Thumb wedding with groom Robert Goggins, and bride Carol Dillingham, walking down aisle in Union Baptist Church
